13
00:00:53,070 --> 00:00:58,860
♫ How long does it take for them to be aware of each other? ♫

14
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:02,450
♫ You are like summer night, ♫

15
00:01:02,450 --> 00:01:06,030
♫ I'm like a little star in the sky, ♫

16
