♫ The caring feeling is so sweet! ♫

20
00:01:26,790 --> 00:01:30,215
[The Best of You in My Mind]

21
00:01:30,215 --> 00:01:33,136
[Episode 9]

22
00:01:33,136 --> 00:01:36,590
[Hum Hum Organic Farm]

23
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,990
[University of Science and Technology, Rongcheng]

24
00:01:46,730 --> 00:01:50,008
Stop the bus, I've lost my phone.

25
00:01:53,109 --> 00:01:54,488
I'll be back shortly.

26
00:01:54,489 --> 00:01:58,168
- Chi-Chi, no need to rush, we'll wait for you.
- Alright.

27
00:02:24,859 --> 00:02:26,079
At last, I've found it.

28
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:28,939
Otherwise, mom wouldn't be able to contact me.

29
00:02:34,859 --> 00:02:36,759
Where's the bus?

30
00:02:37,579 --> 00:02:40,139
Didn't' Nie Yue say that they'd wait for me?

31
00:02:43,859 --> 00:02:45,259
Chi-chi.

32
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:49,379
I was so scared! I thought I was left here all alone.

33
00:02:49,379 --> 00:02:51,899
The driver went to town to refuel; he said he'd wait for us there.

34
00:02:51,899 --> 00:02:55,320
- Let's go and meet up with them
- How?

35
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,800
By that.

36
00:03:01,579 --> 00:03:03,520
I'll take you downtown.

37
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,998
- Thank you.
- Thanks.

38
00:03:10,460 --> 00:03:12,860
The sky here is so blue.

39
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:15,218
The air is so fresh.

40
00:03:15,219 --> 00:03:17,639
The field is so wide.

41
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:23,579
Little girl, come here after you graduate.

42
00:03:23,579 --> 00:03:26,500
The scenery is great in our village.

43
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:28,620
The air is fresh.

44
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:32,200
There are also many animals here.

45
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:35,399
- I'll think about it.
- Alright.

46
00:03:35,399 --> 00:03:39,279
How about I advise our university to organize more fieldwork here every year.

47
00:03:39,279 --> 00:03:41,479
Really? That's great!

48
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:44,180
I'm looking forward to it.

49
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:50,479
I've prepared a birthday present for you.

50
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:52,759
I'll tell you what it is later.

51
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:57,900
You're acting mysterious, but thanks anyway Senior Ye.

52
00:03:57,900 --> 00:04:00,819
Has today been a good day?

53
00:04:00,819 --> 00:04:03,378
Yes. A wonderful day!

54
00:04:03,379 --> 00:04:04,680
Good.

55
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:10,659
Oh, no! I hit a lamb.

56
00:04:13,279 --> 00:04:15,900
It's a little lamb.

57
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:17,540
I think I hit it hard.

58
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:19,779
I think its bones are fractured.

59
00:04:19,779 --> 00:04:22,778
Let's send it back to the farm and give it some basic treatment.

60
00:04:22,778 --> 00:04:25,558
- Let's do it your way.
- Gently!

61
00:04:25,558 --> 00:04:27,999
Be careful!
[Xu Fang]

62
00:04:27,999 --> 00:04:30,978
- Be careful!
- Here!

63
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:38,919
Why isn't she picking up?

64
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:53,139
- Let me use it for a while.
- Give it back!

65
00:04:53,139 --> 00:04:55,980
- Why are you nervous?
- Want me to beat you up?

66
00:04:59,999 --> 00:05:03,498
Since you prepared a present, just give it to her,

67
00:05:03,499 --> 00:05:05,579
then confess and that's it.

68
00:05:05,579 --> 00:05:07,839
I'm anxious that you're taking so long.

69
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:10,479
Just wait until you're in love.

70
00:05:10,479 --> 00:05:12,219
Me?

71
00:05:12,219 --> 00:05:13,900
I'm different.

72
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:16,520
I like to take the initiative.

73
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:21,018
What's wrong? Which girl do you like?

74
00:05:21,018 --> 00:05:22,600
I'm not telling you.

75
00:05:24,119 --> 00:05:26,219
Come down!

76
00:05:27,060 --> 00:05:30,358
- Who is it? Tell me!
- No way!

77
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:36,619
Don't do that! I just went to the toilet.

78
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:53,830
[Anthropology]

79
00:05:57,499 --> 00:06:00,138
It's here! The first aid kit's here.

80
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:03,778
- That's great!
- Don't be afraid! We'll get it done soon.

81
00:06:03,778 --> 00:06:05,999
It doesn't hurt.

82
00:06:08,219 --> 00:06:09,539
No pain, right?

83
00:06:09,540 --> 00:06:12,678
- I think we can only do this much for today.
- Almost done.

84
00:06:12,678 --> 00:06:16,098
Send it to a vet tomorrow to see if there are other injuries.

85
00:06:16,098 --> 00:06:19,660
- Alright. Thanks!
- No worries.

86
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:23,778
It's getting late! I'll take you to the station when you're done.

87
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:29,418
Senior Ye, what time is it now?

88
00:06:30,719 --> 00:06:33,899
How long will it take to get there?

89
00:06:33,899 --> 00:06:36,999
I think we'll be there soon. Are you in a rush?

90
00:06:36,999 --> 00:06:40,040
I'm going to have dinner with my mom.

91
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:45,318
[Mom: Chi-chi, I have surgery. I need to go to the hospital tonight]

92
00:06:45,318 --> 00:06:47,279
[Let's meet another day.]

93
00:06:48,539 --> 00:06:51,379
I made her wait too long.

94
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:03,580
[Outpatient Lobby]

95
00:07:13,100 --> 00:07:15,260
Will you be okay on your own?

96
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:17,579
Yes, Senior Ye! You should go back and rest.

97
00:07:17,579 --> 00:07:20,420
I'll take a cab back after I see my mom.

98
00:07:21,260 --> 00:07:24,810
Alright! Call me if there's anything.

99
00:07:25,539 --> 00:07:26,819
Bye.

100
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:42,599
Mom, I'm back! I'll go to see you at your dorm.

101
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:49,320
[Outpatient Lobby]

102
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:52,660
Mom!

103
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:09,440
Hello! Are you looking for someone?

104
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,159
My mom is Zheng Fang-fang.

105
00:08:11,159 --> 00:08:14,159
I think she doing surgery, so I'm waiting for her here.

106
00:08:14,159 --> 00:08:17,879
Doctor Zheng? She is not staying here.

107
00:08:19,659 --> 00:08:21,400
She's not?

108
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:25,118
Yes, she goes home usually.

109
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:27,760
Home?

110
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:46,339
Don't wait for her!

111
00:08:47,417 --> 00:08:50,579
She went to downtown to find her mother.

112
00:08:57,339 --> 00:08:59,480
She's not into you.

113
00:09:04,300 --> 00:09:06,680
It's none of your business.

114
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:09,980
At least, she was happy with me today.

115
00:09:13,459 --> 00:09:15,980
It's just a single birthday.

116
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:31,300
[Anesthesia and Operation Center]

117
00:09:42,999 --> 00:09:44,640
Sister Fang?

118
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:47,490
You must be tired.

119
00:09:47,499 --> 00:09:49,140
Yes, I am.

120
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:51,818
There's a food delivery here just now, did you order it?

121
00:09:51,818 --> 00:09:53,778
That's right! I forgot about it.

122
00:09:53,779 --> 00:09:56,718
- I put it in your office.
- Thank you.

123
00:09:56,718 --> 00:09:59,658
I saw a girl when I was at our dorms just now.

124
00:09:59,659 --> 00:10:01,419
She said she's your daughter.

125
00:10:01,419 --> 00:10:03,790
- My daughter?
- Yes.

126
00:10:04,518 --> 00:10:06,279
Did you tell her anything?

127
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:09,020
I didn't tell her much.

128
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:11,099
Doctor Liu, a patient is waiting for you.

129
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:13,398
- I'll be going.
- All right.

130
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,500
[Zheng Fang-fang]

131
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:46,000
Hello! It's bad.

132
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,000
Chi-chi came to our hospital dorms.

133
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,900
She may find out that I've been lying.

134
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:51,400
Why are you so careless?

135
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:54,500
I didn't know she would come here suddenly.

136
00:10:55,139 --> 00:10:57,998
- Did you send me a text?
- When did I send you a text?

137
00:10:57,998 --> 00:11:00,300
I don't have your WeChat.

138
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:02,300
Hold on!

139
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,400
I got it now.

140
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:19,300
- Chi-chi pretended to be you and sent me a text.
- When was that?

141
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:21,200
Did you say anything?

142
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:23,300
I don't think so.

143
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,000
What should we do now?

144
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:28,900
Let me think about it.

145
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:04,700
How was your birthday celebration with your mother yesterday?

146
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,000
Come here!

147
00:12:17,900 --> 00:12:21,800
Da Xue, let me tell you a story.

148
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:30,900
Senior Ye, what are you doing?

149
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:33,900
I'm telling Da Xue a story.

150
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:40,500
I said that I have an extremely smart, beautiful and cute friend.

151
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:42,400
Her name is Lin Xichi.

152
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:45,000
I think there's something on her mind,

153
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:48,100
but I don't know if she is willing to tell me.

154
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,200
I'll always listen to her.

155
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,800
Thank you, Senior Ye.

156
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:02,200
Do you have something on your mind?

157
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:23,600
I need to call someone back.

158
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,800
[Fang-fang, it's been a while.]

159
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,600
[From Lin Chang Ge: When I replied to you previously]

160
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:40,300
[I was thinking about the way you left in a hurry]

161
00:13:40,300 --> 00:13:44,200
[I got angry and said something bad. I'm sorry!]

162
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:48,800
[Your WeChat reminded me of the moments we had in university]

163
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:53,500
[I can still smell the jujube juice in the enamel cup]

164
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:57,900
[I started making jujube juice for Chi-chi after that]

165
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,400
Chi-chi, you're back?

166
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,000
Here.

167
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,600
Drink it!

168
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,500
It's hot!

169
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:14,400
Look! Why didn't you arrange your shoes?

170
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:20,400
Let me do it!

171
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:23,300
I'm making lunch for you.

172
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,800
[Countdown to the College Entrance Examination]

173
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:51,000
Chi-chi, I heard you came to the dorm.

174
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,400
Why didn't you tell me before you came?

175
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:56,200
I found a place to move into a few days ago.

176
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:59,600
I didn't get to tell you, so you came here for nothing.

177
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:04,200
Let me celebrate your birthday when I have time later.

178
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:07,600
I'll definitely be on time.

179
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,700
Okay, then let's meet up in a few days.

180
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:12,300
- See you!
- Bye-bye.

181
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:29,000
But, Mom can never hear these words from dad.

182
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:32,600
Since dad hasn't forgotten about mom,

183
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:37,400
I should make them meet each other and let him tell mom in person.

184
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:39,200
Chang Ge.

185
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:43,000
I wonder if you can come to Rong City.

186
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:47,000
I want to meet up with you.

187
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,400
Hello.

188
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:14,400
Chi-chi asked me to go to Rong City in WeChat.

189
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,900
- How did you reply?
- I haven't replied yet.

190
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:18,600
What should we do?

191
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:21,100
You're asking what we should do? Reject it, of course!

192
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:22,600
I'm too busy.

193
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,600
I can't even have a proper meal.

194
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:27,900
I don't have time to play along with your farce.

195
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:32,000
She asked for that because she thinks there's still hope.

196
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:35,500
Look! She knew that you are not staying at the dorm.

197
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:37,400
Now we need to get rid of her concerns.

198
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:39,800
Lin Chang Ge, what do you mean?

199
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:41,800
How long do I need to keep it from her?

200
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:45,100
Could she still forgive me if she found out that I've always been lying to her?

201
00:16:45,100 --> 00:16:48,300
Why do I have to be the evil one?

202
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:53,100
- Hello.
- Dr. Zheng, there's an emergency patient.

203
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:55,400
Okay, I'm coming.

204
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:58,400
- I'm hanging up.
- Let's meet at Rong City.

205
00:17:12,100 --> 00:17:15,200
You looked sad when you went out, but you came back looking happy.

206
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:17,400
Is it good news or bad news?

207
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:20,100
My dad promised to come to Rong City.

208
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:24,300
Well, I have good news for you.

209
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:26,200
What is it?

210
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:33,800
Our pet shop is willing to offer you a part-time job.

211
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:38,600
I thought of you when the manager said they needed extra help.

212
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:41,100
I know it's your ambition to be a veterinarian.

213
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:43,600
So this is the best place for you to learn.

214
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:46,800
I also think it's the most fitting birthday present for you.

215
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:50,600
I... Can I really stay here?

216
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:53,600
This one... Of course!

217
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:57,200
That's great! I have a job.

218
00:17:59,900 --> 00:18:04,700
- But...
- Do you have other concerns?

219
00:18:25,579 --> 00:18:28,578
Look! Lin Xichi is on the university's blog again.

220
00:18:28,578 --> 00:18:31,600
- Did she embarrass herself again?
- It's a good thing this time.

221
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:35,100
It says that she saved a lamb while interning at the farm

222
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:38,500
and sent the lamb back afterwards; they even sent her a banner of appreciation.

223
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:40,600
[Reward for a Doer of Good Deeds]

224
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,600
Along with them, there's also...

225
00:18:44,600 --> 00:18:48,000
[Another student, Ye Shao Wen provided help...]

226
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:53,500
Well... Why does Ye Shao Wen appear everywhere?

227
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:57,400
The girl with short hair who saved the lamb with Senior Ye.

228
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,800
Is she pretty or cute?

229
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:01,400
Average, I guess.

230
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:03,500
Then why does Senior Ye like her?

231
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:05,200
I heard they saved a lamb together.

232
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:08,400
I could've met the lamb, too, if I was lucky.

233
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,800
Forget it!

234
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:14,100
Miss, this is for you.

235
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,400
- Thank you!
-You're welcome!

236
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,700
What?

237
00:19:26,300 --> 00:19:29,800
- What's wrong with him?
- It's so sticky.

238
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:36,500
[Parcel and Mail: Dorm 107 Lin Xichi]

239
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:41,900
Ma'am, I'm Lin Xichi from dorm 107.

240
00:19:41,900 --> 00:19:44,000
Is there a parcel for me?

241
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:49,800
Was it delivered?

242
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:52,900
A very handsome guy brought it.

243
00:19:52,900 --> 00:19:56,600
It's wrapped nicely! Senior Ye is so considerate.

244
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:58,600
Thank you.

245
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,000
Relaxing, right?

246
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:09,118
What are both of you doing? Not allow me to get into my dorm?

247
00:20:09,118 --> 00:20:10,600
I heard something.

248
00:20:10,600 --> 00:20:15,100
I heard that you had a passionate night with Senior Ye yesterday.

249
00:20:15,100 --> 00:20:17,600
Why haven't you told us?

250
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:20,400
I-I-I didn't get a chance to tell you both.

251
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,800
You can tell us anytime.

252
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:27,700
It's more or less the same as what the blog wrote.

253
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:30,900
Did Senior Ye create any romantic atmosphere?

254
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:37,000
There's something! What's this?

255
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:39,800
- It's from Senior Ye.
- Let me see!

256
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:42,400
- I'll open it for you.
- Be gentle!

257
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:46,439
Don't break it!

258
00:20:47,840 --> 00:20:51,019
- A mug?
- A mug.

259
00:20:51,019 --> 00:20:53,660
It symbolizes a lifetime. (TN: bèizi -- a homonym of a cup and a lifetime)

260
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:58,258
The first to get a boyfriend in our dorm is appearing.

261
00:20:58,258 --> 00:21:01,959
Stop this nonsense! Leave me alone.

262
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:06,119
There's a book, too.

263
00:21:06,119 --> 00:21:07,819
Taking a picture!

264
00:21:15,740 --> 00:21:17,478
- You're back?
- Taking a bath?

265
00:21:17,478 --> 00:21:19,060
Yes.

266
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:32,140
I have that book too.

267
00:21:55,219 --> 00:21:59,198
- There's a big fool in here.
- A girl in love.

268
00:21:59,198 --> 00:22:01,640
A big fool!

269
00:22:02,199 --> 00:22:05,518
- You're the big fool.
- A big fool!

270
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:20,919
Don't you have class? Why are you here?

271
00:22:23,560 --> 00:22:26,200
I have something to tell you.

272
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:28,100
Just say it!

273
00:22:30,410 --> 00:22:32,118
I found a part-time job.

274
00:22:32,118 --> 00:22:35,860
I don't think I can help out anymore but I got a replacement.

275
00:22:35,860 --> 00:22:38,019
The coach agreed.

276
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:41,000
What part-time job?

277
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:45,080
Senior Ye introduced me to a pet shop.

278
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:03,200
Why did Lin Xichi come to you?

279
00:23:07,019 --> 00:23:09,259
I need your help.

280
00:23:10,100 --> 00:23:16,218
[Pupurazzi]

281
00:23:16,219 --> 00:23:19,200
There are some exotic animals in the shop, such as

282
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:22,700
lizards, snakes and hedgehogs.

283
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:24,859
This is the grooming center.

284
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:28,838
We have professional groomers to groom and style pets.

285
00:23:28,838 --> 00:23:31,120
How can I help?

286
00:23:31,760 --> 00:23:33,460
Follow me!

287
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:42,438
Everyone needs to start from the basics.

288
00:23:42,438 --> 00:23:45,400
You can help us to clean the cages.

289
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:50,400
No problem! Leave it to me.

290
00:24:18,279 --> 00:24:20,699
Let me introduce a new member

291
00:24:20,699 --> 00:24:23,700
who will replace Lin Xichi as an assistant.

292
00:24:24,380 --> 00:24:26,459
Introduce yourself.

293
00:24:26,459 --> 00:24:28,599
Hello! I'm Nie Yue.

294
00:24:28,599 --> 00:24:31,419
I'll be taking care of everyone from now.

295
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:34,538
Xu Fang, Lin Xichi won't come here anymore?

296
00:24:34,539 --> 00:24:37,318
Will she prepare snacks for us?

297
00:24:37,318 --> 00:24:39,419
Will she be as considerate as Lin Xichi?

298
00:24:39,419 --> 00:24:41,119
Don't worry! I do know.

299
00:24:41,119 --> 00:24:45,260
Yao Wang, you love snacks but only a bag of chips every week.

300
00:24:45,260 --> 00:24:47,840
Also, Yu Tong, I know you sweat easily,

301
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:51,119
so I've prepared extra towels for you.

302
00:24:51,119 --> 00:24:54,438
Don't worry! Chi-chi has told me everything.

303
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:06,538
All right! Let's welcome Nie Yue to our archery team.

304
00:25:20,899 --> 00:25:24,579
Tired? Come! Have a drink and take a break.

305
00:25:24,579 --> 00:25:27,059
- Thanks!
- Let me do it.

306
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:32,418
Don't carry it like that! It reeks of sweat.

307
00:25:32,418 --> 00:25:35,538
It's alright! Of course, I know...

308
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:42,080
Whose is this? It stinks.

309
00:25:44,179 --> 00:25:47,239
I didn't expect it's tough to be an assistant.

310
00:25:47,239 --> 00:25:49,518
Chi-chi used to say she's tired when she came back.

311
00:25:49,518 --> 00:25:52,239
Now, I realized that being an assistant is tough.

312
00:25:52,239 --> 00:25:55,999
It's alright! I won't let you suffer as long as you are here.

313
00:26:02,220 --> 00:26:04,379
Can I put the bucket here?

314
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:08,119
By the way, Nie Yue,

315
00:26:08,119 --> 00:26:11,320
I have something to discuss with you.

316
00:26:12,780 --> 00:26:17,559
I'm very happy that you joined us but I feel that when Lin Xichi is not in the team,

317
00:26:17,559 --> 00:26:21,579
Xu Fang is not his usual self.

318
00:26:21,579 --> 00:26:23,680
So, I think...

319
00:26:24,620 --> 00:26:27,940
Actually, how Xu Fang feels about Chi-Chi,

320
00:26:27,940 --> 00:26:30,939
- it's impossible for me not to see.
- Right?

321
00:26:30,939 --> 00:26:34,038
But Chi-chi has a choice.

322
00:26:34,038 --> 00:26:36,230
If she likes Ye Shao Wen, I also...

323
00:26:36,230 --> 00:26:40,250
She-she-she can't... If she likes Ye Shao Wen, Xu Fang...

324
00:26:40,250 --> 00:26:43,719
it would kill him, he'd spend the rest of his life alone.

325
00:26:43,719 --> 00:26:45,458
No, I just believe that

326
00:26:45,458 --> 00:26:48,619
you'll see if we can come up with something,

327
00:26:48,619 --> 00:26:50,580
so Lin Xichi can be here more often?

328
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:52,580
She can help you with your work.

329
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:57,459
It's important to let them see each other,

330
00:26:57,459 --> 00:27:00,679
so they won't forget each other, right?

331
00:27:02,300 --> 00:27:04,339
I get it!

332
00:27:09,100 --> 00:27:11,400
It's done basically.

333
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:16,019
- Your skill is getting better.
- Good boy, good boy!

334
00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:19,100
It's all right!

335
00:27:19,980 --> 00:27:22,300
He's getting impatient.

336
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:24,540
It's done!

337
00:27:24,540 --> 00:27:28,139
Good boy, good boy! We're done.

338
00:27:34,639 --> 00:27:38,480
The archery team will laugh at me if they see me.

339
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,800
Thank you, senior.

340
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:03,479
I didn't think that she'd ask you to clean cages.

341
00:28:04,300 --> 00:28:07,059
Maybe she thinks I'm new to this.

342
00:28:07,819 --> 00:28:09,719
Let me help you.

343
00:28:23,820 --> 00:28:26,639
Here! Be careful!

344
00:28:32,311 --> 00:28:35,418
♪ It's not that difficult ♪

345
00:28:35,418 --> 00:28:38,539
Will you come again tomorrow?
♪ Making a choice is not so difficult. ♪

346
00:28:38,539 --> 00:28:40,280
Of course!

347
00:28:41,219 --> 00:28:45,158
♪ It’s all warm and scattered expectation. ♪

348
00:28:45,158 --> 00:28:47,739
The day after tomorrow?

349
00:28:47,739 --> 00:28:51,438
The day after that? Next week, next month, you'll always come?

350
00:28:51,438 --> 00:28:53,818
♪ Making a decision is not so difficult. ♪

351
00:28:53,819 --> 00:28:56,060
I'll always come over in the future.

352
00:28:56,060 --> 00:29:02,840
♪ Nothing more than day and night mediocre bravery. ♪

353
00:29:06,020 --> 00:29:07,759
What are you doing here?

354
00:29:07,759 --> 00:29:09,359
I... just want to have a look.

355
00:29:09,359 --> 00:29:13,279
- It's dangerous to go inside during their practice.
- I just want to look for a little bit.

356
00:29:13,279 --> 00:29:15,079
♪ They're upset all the time ♪

357
00:29:15,080 --> 00:29:17,499
♪ It's actually not that difficult. ♪

358
00:29:17,499 --> 00:29:20,738
Yue Yue, does the archery team still have any vacancies?

359
00:29:20,738 --> 00:29:23,579
Let me join as well; I want to help, too.

360
00:29:23,579 --> 00:29:25,239
One is enough, Miss!

361
00:29:25,239 --> 00:29:27,738
My princess, don't get into Lin Xi Chi's troubles.

362
00:29:27,738 --> 00:29:29,899
It's tiring.

363
00:29:29,899 --> 00:29:34,300
I said I'm here to help, actually,

364
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:36,620
you're the one who is helping me.

365
00:29:36,620 --> 00:29:40,319
♪ Even if it hurts, being together or not, ♪

366
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:44,900
♪ those are all the best moments of life! ♪

367
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:49,000
Zi Dan, let me tell you the truth.

368
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:53,819
I knew that you have feelings for him.

369
00:29:53,819 --> 00:29:56,950
However, I suspect that

370
00:29:56,950 --> 00:29:59,200
Xu Fang won't yield.

371
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:02,700
You will get hurt if you insist on it.

372
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:07,880
Both you and Chi-chi are my friends, so I'm not being biased.

373
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:11,999
Just that...you are sensitive but you should know

374
00:30:11,999 --> 00:30:14,880
that the person Xu Fang likes...

375
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:17,899
is Lin Xichi.

376
00:30:18,580 --> 00:30:21,280
Xi Chi already has Senior Ye.

377
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:47,218
- I'm back.
-Chi-chi.

378
00:30:48,679 --> 00:30:50,530
Chi-chi?

379
00:30:50,979 --> 00:30:53,259
How do you feel about working with Senior Ye?

380
00:30:53,260 --> 00:30:55,200
Have there been any developments?

381
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:59,779
I'm not sure if there have been any developments.

382
00:30:59,779 --> 00:31:03,200
I just know that I'm exhausted.

383
00:31:05,679 --> 00:31:08,639
Sit up straight! Let me give you a massage.

384
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:14,140
Zi Dan, tell me!

385
00:31:14,140 --> 00:31:18,879
Will you feel tired when you're getting along with a guy?

386
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:25,439
When I'm with Senior Ye I feel really tired

387
00:31:25,439 --> 00:31:29,158
but when I'm with Xu Fang I feel very relaxed.

388
00:31:29,158 --> 00:31:30,960
I can do whatever I want.

389
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,759
That's how it is.

390
00:31:32,759 --> 00:31:36,160
Senior Ye treats you so nicely.

391
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:38,880
He does! He sent me back

392
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:41,470
and bought me some chestnuts.

393
00:31:41,479 --> 00:31:43,480
Do you want one?

394
00:31:44,559 --> 00:31:47,580
So why did you say that there were no developments?

395
00:31:47,580 --> 00:31:52,039
Because I was so tired that I wasn't in the mood to do anything.

396
00:31:52,039 --> 00:31:54,700
Even if he is so handsome.

397
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:57,239
Actually, I think what you felt is correct.

398
00:31:57,239 --> 00:32:00,599
But it's normal to get nervous

399
00:32:00,599 --> 00:32:03,060
when you're with the person you like.

400
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:05,999
You want to present yourself in the best way

401
00:32:05,999 --> 00:32:08,219
and not to disappoint him.

402
00:32:08,219 --> 00:32:10,990
That is why you feel restrained,

403
00:32:10,990 --> 00:32:13,990
unnatural and cautious.

404
00:32:14,559 --> 00:32:16,719
It's totally fine.

405
00:32:18,179 --> 00:32:19,620
Is that so?

406
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:23,059
Ask anyone! They'll give you the same answer.

407
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:29,019
What's wrong with you?

408
00:32:29,019 --> 00:32:31,460
Why do you feel tired, too?

409
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:33,700
- What's wrong?
- What happened?

410
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:36,080
I'm not going to the archery team anymore.

411
00:32:36,080 --> 00:32:37,859
Xu Fang is a devil.

412
00:32:37,859 --> 00:32:39,678
What? Did he bully you?

413
00:32:39,678 --> 00:32:43,758
He exploited me and used me as a slave, asking me to do everything.

414
00:32:43,758 --> 00:32:45,899
I did way more than you.

415
00:32:45,900 --> 00:32:48,300
I'm not going anymore

416
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:50,758
It's fine! Wait for me! I'll get even with him for you.

417
00:32:50,758 --> 00:32:53,559
- You said it!
- I said it.

418
00:32:54,360 --> 00:32:58,020
Give me a massage in return for my love to you.

419
00:32:58,020 --> 00:33:00,240
I'm in a rush, so I'm heading out.

420
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:02,239
It's going to rain.

421
00:33:06,419 --> 00:33:09,519
She came back sad and went out happy?

422
00:33:09,519 --> 00:33:11,799
Is she up to something?

423
00:33:17,679 --> 00:33:19,878
Nie Yue, you're so smart.

424
00:33:19,878 --> 00:33:22,540
You knew it would rain and brought an umbrella.

425
00:33:22,540 --> 00:33:25,160
The weather in Rong City is changing.

426
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:29,519
- I always have an umbrella with me.
- Smart!

427
00:33:29,519 --> 00:33:32,659
Oh, let me tell you! My plan worked well.

428
00:33:32,659 --> 00:33:35,138
I told Chi-chi that Xu Fang was exploiting me.

429
00:33:35,138 --> 00:33:38,318
- She'll find Xu Fang tomorrow.
- So smart!

430
00:33:38,318 --> 00:33:40,080
You're great!

431
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:42,079
Let me find some friends.

432
00:33:42,079 --> 00:33:44,198
I'll pay and get you a signed picture of Hei Yu.

433
00:33:44,198 --> 00:33:46,699
No-No need! You don't have to.

434
00:33:46,699 --> 00:33:48,979
I have many.

435
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:54,118
- You already have it?
- Thank you, anyway.

436
00:33:54,118 --> 00:33:55,860
You're welcome!

437
00:33:58,350 --> 00:33:59,899
It's raining heavily.

438
00:33:59,899 --> 00:34:02,579
There's only an umbrella, how will I go back?

439
00:34:03,359 --> 00:34:06,059
- That's right.
- Right.

440
00:34:07,639 --> 00:34:10,018
Why don't I leave the umbrella for you?

441
00:34:10,018 --> 00:34:12,019
- I'll run back, it's nearer.
- No.

442
00:34:12,019 --> 00:34:13,599
Let's forget it. Forget it!

443
00:34:13,599 --> 00:34:17,579
Why don't I send you back first before I go back?

444
00:34:17,579 --> 00:34:19,460
That works!

445
00:34:19,460 --> 00:34:21,059
Let's go!

446
00:34:32,430 --> 00:34:35,100
Lin Xichi, you come back!

447
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:39,860
Xu Fang, did you exploit Nie Yue?

448
00:34:40,919 --> 00:34:43,538
Did you get angry because I left?

449
00:34:43,538 --> 00:34:47,178
Vent your anger on me! Why did you bully Nie Yue?

450
00:34:47,178 --> 00:34:50,639
I'll beat you up if you bully her again.

451
00:34:51,820 --> 00:34:53,559
How's work at the pet shop?

452
00:34:53,559 --> 00:34:55,919
2,000 yuan a month.

453
00:34:55,919 --> 00:34:58,498
The manager hired me right away because I'm passionate,

454
00:34:58,499 --> 00:35:00,400
love small animals and

455
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:02,460
have the necessary qualities.

456
00:35:02,460 --> 00:35:05,332
- You're not suitable.
- Why is that?

457
00:35:05,332 --> 00:35:07,439
You have no qualities.

458
00:35:09,100 --> 00:35:12,079
You can't step on me. Enough, enough!

459
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:15,120
Come here!

460
00:35:25,819 --> 00:35:29,460
I left the archery team and helped someone else.

461
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:32,419
I helped your brother and granted Nie Yue's wish.

462
00:35:32,419 --> 00:35:34,700
Talking nonsense again?

463
00:35:37,579 --> 00:35:41,058
The relationship is getting better between my serious roommate

464
00:35:41,059 --> 00:35:43,299
and the carefree Jiang Zheng Xu.

465
00:35:43,299 --> 00:35:45,120
Are you blind?

466
00:35:46,599 --> 00:35:48,919
Focused and sincere.

467
00:35:48,919 --> 00:35:52,038
You need to be focused in a relationship, right?

468
00:35:52,038 --> 00:35:54,839
No, I'm talking about archery.

469
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:07,060
Lin Xichi!

470
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:08,819
Wait!

471
00:36:12,019 --> 00:36:15,419
Wait! Can you quit the job in the pet shop?

472
00:36:15,419 --> 00:36:17,980
I've promised Senior Ye.

473
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:21,719
Defeat me and I'll let you go.

474
00:36:21,719 --> 00:36:23,598
Can you not joke around?

475
00:36:23,598 --> 00:36:25,520
Do you think I'm joking?

476
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:27,260
Come here!

477
00:36:30,240 --> 00:36:31,740
Come on!

478
00:36:35,119 --> 00:36:37,459
Three, two, one, start!

479
00:36:41,839 --> 00:36:45,559
Even my dog gave me a handicap when we used to play games.

480
00:36:49,499 --> 00:36:51,099
You...

481
00:36:51,919 --> 00:36:54,079
You... What you?

482
00:36:56,820 --> 00:36:58,940
Don't forget that you lost.

483
00:36:58,940 --> 00:37:01,058
I'll work there even if I lost. Move!

484
00:37:01,058 --> 00:37:03,339
Make way! Don't block me.

485
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:33,239
Do you know what time it is?

486
00:37:33,239 --> 00:37:36,058
I'm sorry! I had something at school.

487
00:37:36,058 --> 00:37:39,299
It's only your second day, yet you came so late to work.

488
00:37:39,299 --> 00:37:41,679
There are strict rules in the company.

489
00:37:41,679 --> 00:37:46,619
Don't think I would be lenient because the son of our boss introduced you.

490
00:37:46,619 --> 00:37:49,600
- The son of the boss?
- Yes.

491
00:37:49,600 --> 00:37:52,400
Ye Shao Wen is the son of our boss.

492
00:37:53,919 --> 00:37:55,600
One last chance!

493
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:57,979
I hope you cherish it.

494
00:37:58,639 --> 00:38:03,200
I'm sorry! I'll work hard.

495
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:05,080
Get to work!

496
00:38:26,190 --> 00:38:29,719
[Lin Xichi, since you left, Xu Fang has been in a bad mood.]

497
00:38:29,719 --> 00:38:31,879
[What's going on between the two of you.]

498
00:38:36,830 --> 00:38:40,579
Lin Xichi! What's the meaning of this?

499
00:38:40,579 --> 00:38:42,519
- I'm sorry!
- I can't scold you for being late?

500
00:38:42,519 --> 00:38:45,720
Are you throwing tantrums now?

501
00:38:45,720 --> 00:38:50,279
I know you don't want to clean cages but everyone starts from here.

502
00:38:50,279 --> 00:38:53,899
No one gets a special treatment around here.

503
00:38:53,899 --> 00:38:56,039
Being passionate is not enough.

504
00:38:56,039 --> 00:38:58,760
You need to be responsible, too. Understand?

505
00:39:05,630 --> 00:39:07,439
Lin Xichi!

